In connection with the outbreak of COVID: In connection with the outbreak of COVID-19, many people have been tested for the virus, but due to lack of resources, the overwhelming majority have not been tested. It is therefore assumed that there are large missing numbers here in connection with the outbreak.
Using self-report, you can get a better: Using self-report, you can get a better picture of how many people have symptoms without exposing health workers to potential contamination hazards and without using up valuable infection control equipment that is already in short supply. We at BustByte, well helped by other volunteers, have created this tool in response to
as an attempt to chart these numbers.
